TASK_DESCRIPTION=The task list in the Go TUI is hard to scan. Cards are too tall, lines everywhere, titles too large, IDs too prominent. Clean it up:

1. Reposition task ID — make it subtle (right-aligned or small prefix), not the dominant element
2. Make task titles more compact — less visual space per card
3. Reduce excessive lines/borders — the list has too many separator lines, make it cleaner
4. Improve visual hierarchy: status + title primary, ID + metadata secondary
5. Overall: fewer lines, more compact cards, easier to scan

Also clean up the task detail/inspect view — too many lines and visual noise there too. Make it clean and nice.

Reference screenshot: /home/doey/.claude/projects/-home-doey-doey/c38e11ff-bafe-4c3c-87d4-240f480fc8de/tool-results/webfetch-1775111570127-xztay3.png

Go TUI code is in tui/ directory.
